snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Greymoor - Official Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
The Elder Scrolls: Greymoor is the newest expansion for The Elder Scrolls Online where players will explore the Dark Heart of Skyrim.

The Greymoor expansion will be released on May 18, 2020, for PC and June 2, 2020, for PS4 and Xbox One.

#ign #gaming #eso
